{% extends '/layout.html.twig' %}

{% block body %}
    <h1>Error Loading Application</h1>
    <p>Sorry, an error occurred while loading the application.</p>

    {% if 'development' == env %}
        <h2>Probable cause</h2>
        <p>Possibly an issue with MongoDB either not being installed or installed but not running.</p>

        <h2>Details</h2>
        <p>{{ message }}</p>

        <h2>Solution</h2>
        <p>If the above details refer to a connection error, please try the following:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>If you followed the 'Quick Start for existing platforms' instructions, revisit the <a href="https://github.com/joindin/joindin-web2#quick-start-for-existing-platforms">MongoDB installation instructions on Github</a></li>
            <li>If you used the project's vagrant installation method, try running <code>vagrant halt</code> followed by <code>vagrant up</code> to reload the virtual machine</li>
            <li>If you need help to solve the problem, drop into the <a href="irc://irc.freenode.net/joind.in">joind.in irc channel on freenode</a></li>
        </ul>
    {% endif %}
{%  endblock %}